This folder is used to store configuration files.

These files are used while developing or deploying your Django project, so mainly they are webserver configurations and other configs.

Please note, for security reasons, you should not expose your webserver configuration to the
public, It is highly recommend to NOT include your config files in VCS if your
VCS is publicly accessible (i.e. via GitHub).

1. Links to the social media sites, apps on the store and ios, an to contact us.
2. Email configuration for automated responses.
3. Configuration for the Database
...
...
...
N. other configuration

Configs comes in three formats:
1. text as config.config
2. json as config.json
3. yaml as config.yaml
4. config as settings.ini




